      <description>&lt;p&gt;What is NLP?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have you heard about Neuro Linguistic Programming, or NLP? It&amp;#8217;s an incredibly useful behavioral science that can help you change your life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Developed in the 1970s, it combines techniques from neurology, computer science, and linguistics to help people achieve their potential. Here&amp;#8217;s what it is and how it works.&lt;/p&gt;
